{"tid":1500722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應煲大清拆李小龍故居一事","createTime":"2019-08-24T06:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T18:44:28.000Z","uid":255563,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd83813e9fa64c527e55d2f577d7b4fd2526465","tid":1500722,"uid":255563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:16:57.000Z","msg":"李小龍故居下星期將被清拆改成 中國國學中心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人一定保衛李小龍故居<br />\n因為外國關注一定唔會細<br />\n<br />\n香港人爭取民主期間，誓死保衛華裔美藉、外國知名度極高嘅李小龍 ,係外國人眼中係係好崇高嘅行動<br />\n亦會好有Noise<br />\n<br />\n他日香港建國，李小龍故居保衛戰，相信都會係歷史留低一筆<br />\n<br />\n我哋日日係到講be water<br />\n就係quote龍哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n龍哥人世間最後嘅尊嚴，都要比乜鳩國學中心搶奪 <br />\n我條氣 唔順！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小龍故居下周清拆 擬大馬複製建主題公園<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1573489/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E9%BE%8D%E6%95%85%E5%B1%85%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86-%E6%93%AC%E5%A4%A7%E9%A6%AC%E8%A4%87%E8%A3%BD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1573489%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%25B1%2585%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25A4%2587%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=97be53fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1573489%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%25B1%2585%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586-%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E8%25A4%2587%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E4%25B8%25BB